[If animals have been shipped to the continent, especially France, before
the ban, then it is possible the shipped animals were already incubating
the disease. The disease may be incubating in France. We do not know if
the shipped animals had any contact with the index cases or others.
Although, there is an equal chance the animals had not been exposed.
However, if I were an animal owner in France, I would be wanting to
vaccinate my animals. - Mod.TG
